,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"輕裝上陣去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5ae666d471043da6354b7cc8b73ad074cb6c2b","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:09:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要有港豬捐錢</blockquote><br />\n無人會捐啦"},{"pid":"72e90a6ce16c1245781cadb8b246a87aba2ccd2c","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"果然係外國網先正路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6debf3a27e782f0bb7a8fcf7f91aff7addf998a5","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:29:22.000Z","msg":"無人覺得好假?"},{"pid":"a03acbe0dea05cdaa6f0ded2137723a7b62b3be5","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"四川茂縣山泥傾瀉，至今發現至少10具屍體，仍有93人失蹤。三百多名災民獲安置到小學和酒店暫住。救援人員開闢一條救援通道，搜索失蹤者。<br />\n<br />\n四川應急指揮中心發放在災區高空拍攝的影像。左邊畫面是茂縣山泥傾瀉前的情況，顯示新磨村輪廓非常清晰，而右邊則是災後的畫面，同一個地方基本上已經被沙石覆蓋，附近松坪溝的河道亦變形，改變水流方向。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員疏通一條被泥石堵塞的河道，防止堰塞湖形成，又在新磨村原址用挖掘機打通一條路，集中搜救。由於相信新磨村不少房屋被塌下的泥石推到河邊，救援人員亦在河道兩岸搜救。<br />\n<br />\n救援人員爭分奪秒，趕在救人黃金七十二小時尋找生還者。<br />\n<br />\n星期日早上一度探測到生命跡象，但經過三個幾小時挖掘後，未有傳來好消息。<br />\n<br />\n至於三百多名災民則獲安置到疊溪鎮的小學和白臘寨村的酒店，並接受心理輔導。除了被埋的新磨村受影響，附近的松坪溝景區亦因為山泥傾瀉，對外交通中斷，百幾名遊客一度滯留。民兵徒步進入景區，協助疏散到安全地方。<br />\n<br />\n事發的阿壩州茂縣疊溪鎮，因為連日暴雨引發嚴重山泥傾瀉，為了應付再有崩塌，當局已經設立14個地質、氣象和水務等監測點，全天候監察災場情況。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/595032d96db28c0c2c0d9a42/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fgreaterchina%2F595032d96db28c0c2c0d9a42%2F&d=uqiiUrotIIEMmpeAN6H3AVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=6bc6e65b\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/greaterchina/595032d96db28c0c2c0d9a42/</a>"},{"pid":"a7c7d09a9cba4c82c775f26470344fa72a41265d","tid":300168,"uid":92178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T17:20:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dacea5c7657d0e372b0c52cac68e3a9d34bf473","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69d0e17b40edd8b65e7ee065ebc2c83fd488736","tid":300168,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"條路新掘重有行車線添bo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e675555f95485338b818956aa477020772a9f4","tid":300168,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:48:32.000Z","msg":"旅客黎下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea02a20250070f51d383143a94f03d54dd6f8f54","tid":300168,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"Cosplay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4fac3b23209e91d893414fdd07a6ae4fbfd1ded","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:05:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cosplay<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab17fb6030ac8e516524448d478d09107ae895a","tid":300168,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旅客黎下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有車都唔坐"}]}